      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">PGI 236.207</ph> Pricing Fixed-Price Construction Contracts.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(a)(70) <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Definition</i>: “lump sum” means a single payment of money, as opposed to a series of payments made over time.</p>
         <p outputclass="List3" class="- topic/p ">(i) An example of a line item with lump sum pricing in accordance with DFARS 204.71 is as follows:</p>
         <table frame="none" colsep="0" rowsep="0" class="- topic/table ">
            <tgroup cols="6"
                    colsep="0"
                    rowsep="0"
                    outputclass="Table"
                    class="- topic/tgroup ">
