                  </row>
                  <row rowsep="0" class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">0001</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Repave runway 4 at Joint Base Andrews</p>
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Firm Fixed Price</p>
                        <p class="- topic/p ">PSC: Z1BD</p>
                        <p class="- topic/p ">ACRN: AA</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">525,128</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Square Foot</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">$2.86</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">$1,501,866.08</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
            </tgroup>
         </table>
         <p class="- topic/p ">Note that this allows the contractor to invoice for completed quantities of work, in accordance with <ph xtrc="FARxref" class="- topic/ph ">FAR 32.102</ph> (d), as those are accepted. Progress payments based on estimates of the percentage of completion (see <ph xtrc="FARxref" class="- topic/ph ">FAR 52.232-5</ph>—Payments Under Fixed-Price Construction Contracts) could also occur prior to that point.</p>
